title: Grateful Dead Live at Civic Arena on 1981-11-29
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Friend Of The Devil-> CC Rider, Candyman, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Althea, Looks Like Rain, Might As Well

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Black Peter-> Satisfaction, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: Today once upon a time Frank S was widely known during this time for great tapes. This historical document definitely brings back the room sound in 1981 steel town. Thanks for getting Streeter's tapes to the world. My friends would say that dude tapes and goes to Harvard. Great memory of this day/night.
